description:
This is a two-wire system, no transmitter is needed. Shrouded push button to avoid unintentional actuation, no internal frictional parts, zero power consumption. This hermetically sealed panel mount switch is internally similar to the diver operated submersible switch 1809-100 used in the Pendant Switch, 1810-100 used by Navy Seals for high reliability and performance. Available as a submersible electric proximity switch or a submersible electric limit switch.

Features:
● Ocean submersible diver operated
● Panel mount style
● Insensitivity to ambient pressure to 1,000 psi ambient
● Low hysteresis - as low as 0.020"
● No internal frictional parts
● Zero power consumption
● 316 SS
